5000|$|Near-infrared and Raman {{spectroscopy}} {{are used}} as secondary analysis techniques. For primary analysis, one of the above-mentioned chemical measuring techniques or other, physical measuring techniques are used. The use of <b>chemometrics</b> for data analysis {{is an essential part}} of NIR spectroscopy.|$|E
